    <h1>Welcome to Brass Dragon Archive!</h1>

    <p>For our final project we'll be creating a character database for Fifth Edition Dungeons and Dragons. This will use at least three pages; login, gallery, and edit page. The database will have at least five tables, a User table holding all logins, a Character table holding created characters, and then tables for Races, Classes and Backgrounds holding gameplay information. Users will be able to manipulate Character records assigned with their own unique ID.</p>
